WEBVTT

00:04:27.880 --> 00:04:31.240
Petnajst žensk me je pospremilo
v Reserve Bank of India.

00:04:32.440 --> 00:04:35.456
Naše ženske so uradniku banke povedale:

00:04:35.480 --> 00:04:39.856
"Zavrnili ste nam dovoljenje,
ker ne znamo brati in pisati.

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:42.976
Zavrnili ste nam dovoljenje,
ker smo nepismene.

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:45.816
Ko smo odraščale, ni bilo šol,

00:04:45.840 --> 00:04:48.840
zato nismo odgovorne
za naše pomanjkanje izobrazbe."

00:04:49.640 --> 00:04:52.456
In rekle so: "Ne znamo brati in pisati,

00:04:52.480 --> 00:04:53.856
znamo pa šteti."

00:04:53.880 --> 00:04:55.896
(smeh)

00:04:55.920 --> 00:04:57.776
(aplavz)

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:59.680
In izzvale so uradnika.